Why? Did my aunt say something?

102
00:09:09,710 --> 00:09:13,550
No, it's not that. You also mentioned someone named Tae Ha before.

103
00:09:13,550 --> 00:09:15,400
Who is he?

104
00:09:16,120 --> 00:09:19,620
He's my cousin. Son of that aunt you met.

105
00:09:23,760 --> 00:09:28,560
Listen carefully... If Tae Ha tries to make a move on you, make sure to let me know.

106
00:09:28,560 --> 00:09:30,900
And don't even pretend to know him, no matter what he does.

107
00:09:30,900 --> 00:09:34,500
Also don't listen to anything he says, got it?

108
00:09:34,500 --> 00:09:37,360
I don't even know what he looks like. How can I pretend to know him?

109
00:09:37,360 --> 00:09:38,800
Well, that's good then.

110
00:09:38,800 --> 00:09:42,550
Anyway, don't meet up with him. As soon as you hear that name, pretend you don't know a thing.

111
00:09:42,550 --> 00:09:44,340
Is that clear?

112
00:10:01,510 --> 00:10:03,420
Sorry, I can't take you home.

113
00:10:03,420 --> 00:10:05,890
It's okay, I know you are busy.

114
00:10:05,890 --> 00:10:08,280
Can you go home alone? Take a cab.

115
00:10:08,280 --> 00:10:12,310
Yeah, I was planning to take a cab to Hyeon Jin's shop and find my way home from there.

116
00:10:12,310 --> 00:10:13,840
Good thinking.

117
00:10:13,840 --> 00:10:17,520
I don't know when I'll get off work, but I'll try to get out as soon as I can.

118
00:10:17,520 --> 00:10:21,640
If time allows, I'll take you home.

119
00:10:21,640 --> 00:10:24,230
Sounds good to me.

120
00:10:26,860 --> 00:10:29,480
What colors do you usually wear?

121
00:10:29,480 --> 00:10:30,230
Well, bright tones.

122
00:10:30,230 --> 00:10:32,800
Bright tones? How about this one?

123
00:10:32,800 --> 00:10:35,620
- Your face is very cute so this might...
- Do you have it in a different color?
- (See you over there?)

124
00:10:35,620 --> 00:10:37,810
