213
00:17:21,150 --> 00:17:26,150
No, I, uh, I'm his fan club... president.

214
00:17:26,150 --> 00:17:30,180
Or you can think of me as his... guardian.

215
00:17:30,180 --> 00:17:31,420
But how are you... here?

216
00:17:31,420 --> 00:17:35,200
I'm actually in charge of SH Mall's PR Department.

217
00:17:35,200 --> 00:17:39,530
