220
00:17:47,000 --> 00:17:50,800
Not a problem. It wasn't anything big. It was just a small, mini-concert event here.

221
00:17:50,800 --> 00:17:54,770
Also Ji Su's style fits our company's image well too. So it receives a lot of good responses.

222
00:17:54,770 --> 00:17:56,360
Thank you!

223
00:17:56,360 --> 00:17:58,550
This is so good.

224
00:17:58,550 --> 00:18:00,290
Thank you.

225
00:18:00,290 --> 00:18:04,780
I believe there is another event here next week as well.

226
00:18:04,780 --> 00:18:10,640
Well, I think we are booked with another artist here but we do have openings in Gangnam and Busan.

227
00:18:10,640 --> 00:18:12,620
