228
00:18:16,940 --> 00:18:19,010
Thank you.

229
00:18:44,310 --> 00:18:47,310
Chairman Han seems to visit here often these days.

230
00:18:47,310 --> 00:18:49,890
Ah well, that elder has lots of time

231
00:18:49,890 --> 00:18:52,850
and a lot of ambition.

232
00:18:52,850 --> 00:18:54,630
Work hard.

233
00:19:17,950 --> 00:19:20,290
