236
00:19:25,320 --> 00:19:28,860
Well, I'm the president of his fan club.

237
00:19:28,860 --> 00:19:30,920
See you.

238
00:19:54,610 --> 00:19:56,670
What?

239
00:19:58,860 --> 00:20:01,070
Open the door.

240
00:20:02,140 --> 00:20:03,960
Do you have something to say?

241
00:20:03,960 --> 00:20:06,710
I'll tell you if you open the door.

242
00:20:24,860 --> 00:20:28,370
So tell me what the issue is.

243
00:20:28,370 --> 00:20:29,290
Come on, talk.

244
00:20:29,290 --> 00:20:33,100
I need to know what the issue is so that I can either explain myself or resolve it some other way.

245
00:20:33,100 --> 00:20:34,160
What is the issue?

246
00:20:34,160 --> 00:20:38,190
How many women have you dated?

247
00:20:40,200 --> 00:20:44,230
If it's a short-term it's one month, and if it's long-term it's six months? Was it like that?

248
00:20:44,230 --> 00:20:47,730
Is this a new kind of jealousy or are you just probing me?

249
00:20:47,730 --> 00:20:49,490
Probing.

250
00:20:49,490 --> 00:20:52,070
You just try cheating on me.

251
00:20:54,310 --> 00:20:56,320
Do you think I have time to meet another woman?

252
00:20:56,320 --> 00:20:59,020
I'm busy enough with Kim Da Hyeon alone.

253
00:20:59,020 --> 00:21:00,470
Don't waste your time thinking about that useless kind of stuff.

254
00:21:00,470 --> 00:21:04,570
If you have time to think about things like that, just call me before I call you.

